	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, I am gonna give you guys a quick breakdown, but the question remains...<BR>
<BR>
STR  STA  AGI  DEX  WIS  INT  CHA<BR>
DE Necro:<BR>
60    65    90    85    83    109  60<BR>
Gnome:<BR>
60    70    85    95    67    108  60<BR>
Erudite:<BR>
60    70    70    80    83    117  70<BR>
<BR>
Deciding which race is the best is very complicated, as each has it's own benefits<BR>
and disadvantages.<BR>
<BR>
The Erudite has by far the best intelligence, which is critical to your spellcasting.<BR>
However, should you do any tanking (i.e. to help keep your pet alive longer, I <BR>
have found that very important) you are at a loss with the Erudite with much lower <BR>
AGI and secondary, DEX.<BR>
<BR>
The Dark Elf has the 2nd most INT. at 1 over the Gnome. Not very much difference, <BR>
I imagine at higher levels both will reach the INT cap anyways.<BR>
The Dark Elf however has 5 more AGI, making it a little less likely to be hit in combat.<BR>
I however, prefer not to be hated practically everywhere...<BR>
<BR>
Which leads to the Gnome, which was my final choice (forget humans and iksars, Necros <BR>
are a spellcasting class, and thus suffer from the INT hit.. IMO)<BR>
The Gnomes have a little (5) better STA than the DE's and 10 better DEX, useful until you <BR>
no longer melee (If you ever really stop, your choice...)<BR>
Gnomes are also less hated than Dark Elves and therefore can freely tavel more easily<BR>
(Worship your Invis anyways, for those not so pleasant places)<BR>
Besides being UGLY, these little guys work the best for ME! BTW I love Steamfont...<BR>
<BR>
Be who you want, who knows, maybe with the right items your Iksar Necro will have <BR>
a higher INT than your buddy's Erudite...<BR>
<BR>
Just my 2 pennies (not wasting any more SP than I have to :)<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
